{"tid":2141460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[一家人]周五起經深圳灣入境廣東須持24小時內檢測陰性證明","createTime":"2020-08-05T16:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T17:03:16.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd25d33f70b9e424e1823a723b6619125984a99","tid":2141460,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542056-20200805.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542056-20200805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=2a5ce0e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542056-20200805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b98bf902\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542056-20200805.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東省政府公布，由星期五早上10時起，除了經批准的公務商務豁免人員，以及跨境司機外，其他人經深圳灣及港珠澳大橋口岸入境廣東時，必須持有特區政府認可醫療機構，發出的24小時內有效核酸檢測陰性證明，入境後仍須接受14日強制檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府呼籲市民前往廣東時，必須確保符合相關規定，並預留充足時間過關，否則將不能夠進入廣東；而在折返香港時，更會因為重新進入香港，而要接受強制檢疫14日。"},{"pid":"bdee993600a477d69a375cfdfee4857b34dd0f6c","tid":2141460,"uid":8441,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">而在折返香港時，更會因為重新進入香港，而要接受強制檢疫14日</span><br />\n<br />\n想睇激到藍絲紮紮跳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0bddd4b2e7e3d51d3c8b192cbf10561deebf2a","tid":2141460,"uid":37596,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"撚藍絲撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51061fb2e443ca79cb804de373cefe3698c2d3d8","tid":2141460,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T16:57:25.000Z","msg":"